<item>
            <title>[FELIX-3603] Resources in META-INF/xxx/ fodlers in a signed bundle should be checked</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-3603</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See section 2.3.2 of the OSGi Core spec,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bundles do not support partially signed bundles. The manifest must contain name sections for all resources but should not have entries for resources in the META-INF directory. Signed entries in the META-INF directory must be verified. Sub directories of META-INF must be treated like any other JAR directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12599716">FELIX-3603</key>
            <summary>Resources in META-INF/xxx/ fodlers in a signed bundle should be checked</summary>
