                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13419801" author="gnt" created="Sat, 21 Jul 2012 11:49:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The problem is located in the following method:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/trunk/framework.security/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/framework/security/verifier/BundleDNParser.java#L271&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/felix/blob/trunk/framework.security/src/main/java/org/apache/felix/framework/security/verifier/BundleDNParser.java#L271&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The verifier ignores all META-INF/xxx entries but it should check resources located inside a subfolder of META-INF as specified in the spec.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13420268" author="karlpauls" created="Sun, 22 Jul 2012 18:41:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Good catch. I&apos;ll take care of it. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13422177" author="karlpauls" created="Wed, 25 Jul 2012 11:54:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I added a check which should make this work. Can you please check the current trunk? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13423568" author="gnt" created="Thu, 26 Jul 2012 23:55:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems there is a problem.&lt;br/&gt;
The java.util.jar.JarVerifier class ignores all entries inside the META-INF folder, so even if those are signed, they won&apos;t be verified.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;m investigating a work around.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13423764" author="gnt" created="Fri, 27 Jul 2012 09:24:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed with  &lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1366310&amp;amp;view=rev&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/viewvc?rev=1366310&amp;amp;view=rev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
